Mongo APIs :

 /mongo/login --> POST --> {username: '', password: ''}
 /mongo/register --> POST --> {firstName: '', lastName: '', username: '', password: ''}
 /mongo/userList --> POST --> {}
 /mongo/updateUser --> POST --> {oldPassword: '', newPassword: ''}
 /mongo/removeUser --> POST --> {username: ''}

 /mysql/login --> POST --> {username: '', password: ''}
 /mysql/register --> POST --> {firstName: '', lastName: '', username: '', password: ''}
 /mysql/userList --> POST --> {}
 /mysql/updateUser --> POST --> {oldPassword: '', newPassword: ''}
 /mysql/removeUser --> POST --> {username: ''}
 
 /sp/loginWithSP --> GET --> login screen
 /sp/createUserWithSP --> GET regisration screen
 /sp/allUserWithFilter --> GET users list screen
